<p>All products were designed by a Board-Certified Physical Medicine Specialist for treating painful medical conditions by providing soft comfortable positioning and support.  Intended for use at nighttime while in bed, when bracing and support are still medically advised for the painful medical condition.  More comfortable nighttime bracing helps promote better a sleep pattern and improved healing.</p>
